allegations at Baylor.

01:18.433 --> 01:20.400 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
PAULA LAVIGNE, ESPN: Right.

01:20.400 --> 01:23.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
