people who are familiar with
the NCAA are saying, well, one

03:50.533 --> 03:55.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
way they can get enforcement in
a case involving sexual violence
is to say, OK, are these student

03:57.433 --> 04:01.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
athletes getting an extra
benefit if they are being
diverted from judicial affairs,

04:03.966 --> 04:08.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
